<sense n=""1""><number>1</number><trans> <tr>throw</tr> liquid or s.t. in grains. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Kinsay nagsabwag nímu ug túbig?</i><trans> Who threw water on you? </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sabwági ug balas ang dáub kay misiláub,</i><trans> Throw sand on the fire because it flared up. </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Isabwag ang sinsilyu sa mga bátà,</i><trans> Throw the coins out to the children. </trans></eg>
