<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Samári (samdi) ug diyútay ang pánit arun makaguwà ang nánà,</i><trans> Make a little incision in the skin so that pus can go out. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""1a""><number>1a</number> <itype>[A123S; b8]</itype><trans> manage to inflict a <tr>wound</tr>. </trans>
