<sense n=""2""><number>2</number> <form id=""samad_nga_walay_pagkaaxyu"" lang=""ceb""><abbr expan=""samad"" type=""lemma"">—</abbr> nga walay pagkaáyu</form><trans> <tr>vagina</tr> (lit. the wound that never heals—humorous). </trans>
