<entry><form id=""samaran_samarun_samdan"" lang=""ceb"">samaran, samarun, samdan</form>
<hom role=""n""><pos>n</pos>
<sense n=""0""><trans> the <tr>wounded</tr>. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ang dinunggábay misamput sa tuluy samarun (samaran, samdan),</i><trans> Three were wounded in the stabbing. </trans></eg>
