<sense n=""1a""><number>1a</number><trans> <tr>timely</tr>, <tr>well-timed</tr>. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sapak ang pagabut mu kay tingkaun,</i><trans> You arrived just at the right time. It’s time to eat. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> having just the right qualities. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sapak sad ug láwas si Iyay ug magbáting sut,</i><trans> Iyay has a beautiful body when she wears a bathing suit. </trans></eg>
</sense></hom>
<hom role=""v""><pos>v</pos>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number> <itype>[A12; a4b8]</itype><trans> do s.t. at just the right time. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Nakasapak sad kag baligyà sa ímung mga ipiktus—subídu ang prisyu,</i><trans> You sold your things at just the right time—when the prices went up. </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ug muadtu ka karun masapak (masapakan) nímu ang pista,</i><trans> If you go there now, you’ll be just on time for the fiesta. </trans></eg>
