<hom role=""v""><pos>v</pos>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number> <itype>[AN; b]</itype><trans> take shelter under. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Anhi ku musílung (manílung) sa iláwum sa káhuy,</i><trans> I’ll take shelter under the tree. </trans></eg>
