</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number> <itype>[A]</itype><trans> be more than a certain amount. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ang íyang swildu musubra ug gatus human ug báyad sa mga útang,</i><trans> His salary will be a bit more than a hundred after he pays off his debts. </trans></eg>
