</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number> <itype>[A13]</itype><trans> live only long enough to be seen. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ígù lang nagpasud-ung tung batáa kay usa ra ka búwan sa maháyag,</i><trans> That child lived only long enough to be seen because it died a month after birth.
