<hom role=""v""><pos>v</pos>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number> <itype>[A; b(1)]</itype><trans> set s.t. on fire or touch a flaming brand to it. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ákù na ba ring sugníban ang sagbut?</i><trans> Shall I <tr>set fire</tr> to the trash? </trans></eg>
