<sense n=""2""><number>2</number> <itype>[A2; b6]</itype><trans> enter a trap under water. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Gisuhútan ang búbù ug pawíkan,</i><trans> The fish trap caught a sea turtle. </trans></eg>
</sense></hom>
