<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> <tr>vagabond</tr>, one who just roams about and does nothing. </trans>
</sense></hom>
<hom role=""v""><pos>v</pos>
<sense n=""0""> <itype>[B1]</itype><trans> be, become an idle <tr>wanderer</tr>. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Nagsuhut bágun nang tawhána kay tapulan man mangítag trabáhu,</i><trans> That man became a vagabond because he’s too lazy to look for work. </trans></eg>
