<entry><form id=""panuxhut"" lang=""ceb""><abbr expan=""panúhut"" type=""lemma"">paN-</abbr></form>
<hom role=""n""><pos>n</pos>
<sense n=""0""><trans> muscular <tr>ache</tr> resulting from exposure to damp or draft, esp. during sleep. </trans>
