<hom role=""a""><pos>a</pos>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number><trans> <tr>glaring</tr>, shining with a harsh and uncomfortably bright light. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sulaw kaáyu ang sugà sa awtu,</i><trans> His car has glaring headlights. </trans></eg>
