<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> <tr>disconcerting</tr>, causing loss of composure. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sulaw kaáyu nga ikúyug nátù ang usa ka higála nga átung gikaáway,</i><trans> It is very disconcerting to have s.o. we just had a quarrel with come along with us. </trans></eg>
