<hom role=""n""><pos>n</pos>
<sense n=""0""><trans> <tr>glare</tr>, intensely shining light. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ang sulaw makadáut sa mata,</i><trans> Glare can damage the eyes. </trans></eg>
</sense></hom>
<hom role=""v""><pos>v</pos>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number> <itype>[A; b6(1)]</itype><trans> give off a <tr>glare</tr>. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Musulaw ang línaw inigsílang sa adlaw,</i><trans> The pool gives off a glare when the sun shines. </trans></eg>
