<sense n=""1""><number>1</number> <itype>[A; a12]</itype><trans> <tr>set against</tr>, <tr>attack</tr>. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sulúngun nátù ang Hapun rung gabíi,</i><trans> We will attack the Japs tonight. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number> <itype>[AN2; a12]</itype><trans> go s.w. to look for trouble. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ug sulúngun (sulngun) ka níya sa iskuylahan, itug-an siya sa maistru,</i><trans> If he goes to school to pick a fight with you, report him to the teacher. </trans></eg>
