<sense n=""1a""><number>1a</number> <itype>[C; ac3]</itype><trans> for animals to fight with their horns. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Nagkasúngag ang duha ka kábaw,</i><trans> The two carabaos are <tr>goring</tr> each other. </trans></eg>
