<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ayaw ug sunda nang batasána,</i><trans> Don’t imitate that sort of manners. </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ayawg sunda ímung maguwang nga balirúsu,</i><trans> Don’t be <pb n=""939""/>headstrong like your elder brother. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""3""><number>3</number> <itype>[A2N]</itype><trans> <tr>inherit</tr>. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Siyay musunud (manunud) sa ákung kabtángan,</i><trans> He will inherit my property. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""3a""><number>3a</number> <itype>[A2; b6]</itype><trans> <tr>succeed</tr> in office. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ang bísi mauy musunud ingkásug mamatay ang prisidinti,</i><trans> The vice-president succeeds in office if the president dies. </trans></eg>
</sense></hom>
<entry><form id=""sunud_ug_kasal"" lang=""ceb""><abbr expan=""sunud"" type=""lemma"">—</abbr> ug kasal</form>
<hom>
<sense n=""0""> <itype>[AN]</itype><trans> <tr>sponsor</tr> a wedding. </trans>
