</sense></hom>
<hom role=""n""><pos>n</pos>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number><trans> <tr>the next</tr>, the one following. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sunud simána,</i><trans> Next week. </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sunud ugmà,</i><trans> The day after tomorrow. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""1a""><number>1a</number><trans> the next thing done. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sunud ilúnud ang balátung human sa karni,</i><trans> After the meat, put the beans in next. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> following, according to the. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sunud sa naandan nga batásan,</i><trans> Following the usual custom. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""3""><number>3</number><trans> <tr>next</tr>. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sunud simána,</i><trans> Next week. </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Sunud gulà,</i><trans> Next issue. </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Siya ang sunud nga prisidinti,</i><trans> He will be the next president. </trans></eg>
</sense></hom></entry>
<entry><form id=""suxnud"" lang=""ceb""><abbr expan=""súnud"" type=""lemma"">(←)</abbr></form>
<hom role=""v""><pos>v</pos>
<sense n=""0""> <itype>[C; a12]</itype><trans> be close to each other in a <tr>series</tr>, line or <tr>succession</tr>. </trans>
